    Allowable sample rates (samples per second): 8000,11025,16000,22050,44100 Higher sample rate means higher range of available frequencies.

    Allowable sample sizes, in bits: 8,16 A sample is a single position for the vibrating membrane, and the size of the sample determines the number of possible positions.

Package ogallagher.marketsense Description

A training program that aims to train human users to improve market asset value prediction.

To better take advantage of the human brain's ability to process signals for pattern recognition and classification, it creating a connection between raw market data and the human senses.

See the readme.md file for a fuller explanation.

9 June 2021
Author:
